               <p>I am a constable. I searched the prisoner; I observed him put his hand into his<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178205150007"></xptr> breeches-pocket, take out a shilling, and tuck it into the waistband of his breeches. This is the shilling (producing it).</p>
